OL,6,FOnly 107 court orders designed to
OL,7,Fprotect victims from stalkers have
OL,8,Fbeen used in the ITV Calendar region
OL,9,Fin the last four years ` despite
OL,10,F67,000 reports of unwanted and
OL,11,Fintrusive behaviour.
OL,13,FStalking protection orders (SPOs) were
OL,14,Fintroduced in 2020 as a tool courts
OL,15,Fcould use to crack down on
OL,16,Fperpetrators.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/21
