OL,6,FBut figures obtained by ITV Calendar
OL,7,Fshow just 107 were granted in the
OL,8,Ffirst four years of the scheme across
OL,9,Fthe police forces of Yorkshire,
OL,10,FLincolnshire and Derbyshire.
OL,12,FIn the same time period, there were
OL,13,F67,000 stalking complaints.
OL,15,FBetween 2020 and 2023, Derbyshire
OL,16,FPolice applied for the highest number
OL,17,Fof SPOs in the region, with 73
OL,18,Fapplications.
OL,20,FOf those, 43 were granted.
