OL,6,FThe other forces' figures were as
OL,7,Ffollows:
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire Police said its latest
OL,10,Ffigures show that it has issued 18
OL,11,FSPOs in total to date so far,
OL,12,Fincluding 9 interim orders.
OL,14,FDomestic abuse charity IDAS said there
OL,15,Fwas a lack of understanding among
OL,16,Fpolice of stalking behaviour.
OL,18,FRegional manager Evie Duarte said:
OL,19,F"Unless it's recognised that it's
OL,20,Fstalking then an order isn't going to
OL,21,Fbe applied for.
