OL,6,FWhat are stalking protection orders?
OL,8,FA stalking protection order is made
OL,9,Ffollowing an application to the
OL,10,Fmagistrates' court by police. It is a
OL,11,Fcivil order.
OL,13,FApplications can be made for interim
OL,14,For full orders.
OL,16,FThey are a tool designed either for
OL,17,Fsituations where the offending does
OL,18,Fnot meet the criminal threshold or
OL,19,Fwhere a suspect has been charged.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/21
