OL,6,FHowever, the police and Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service define it as a
OL,8,Fpattern of unwanted, fixated, and
OL,9,Fobsessive behaviour which is intrusive.
OL,11,FIt can include harassment that amounts
OL,12,Fto stalking or stalking that causes
OL,13,Ffear of violence or serious alarm or
OL,14,Fdistress.
OL,16,FThere is no such thing as a "typical"
OL,17,Fstalking perpetrator or a "typical"
OL,18,Fvictim.
