OL,6,FTragedy that prompted actionJThe issue
OL,7,Fof stalking has become increasingly
OL,8,Fhigh-profile following tragedies like
OL,9,Fthe case of Gracie Spinks.
OL,11,FOn the 18 June 21, she was killed by
OL,12,Fformer colleague Michael Sellers, who
OL,13,Fhad become obsessed with her. She was
OL,14,F23.
OL,16,FGracie had previously reported Sellers
OL,17,Fto Derbyshire Police for following
OL,18,Fher, but he was simply given words of
OL,19,Fadvice.
