OL,6,FAfter killing her, Sellers killed
OL,7,Fhimself.
OL,9,FFollowing the inquest into Gracie's
OL,10,Fdeath, Derbyshire Police apologised
OL,11,Ffor its failings committed to changing
OL,12,Fits handling of stalking incidents.
OL,14,FThe force recruited a stalking
OL,15,Fcoordinator, who supports risk
OL,16,Fassessment processes and stalking
OL,17,Finvestigations. A team which
OL,18,Fspecifically deals with civil orders
OL,19,Fwas also created.
